giftCards.name: Get 50% Off on KFC
giftCards.desc: Get 50% off at any KFC store on shop for 999 and above.KFC, also known as Kentucky Fried Chicken, is an American fast food restaurant chain headquartered in Louisville, Kentucky that specializes in fried chicken. It is the world's second-largest restaurant chain (as measured by sales) after McDonald's, with 22,621 locations globally in 136 countries as of December 2018. The chain is a subsidiary of Yum! Brands, a restaurant company that also owns the Pizza Hut, Taco Bell, and WingStreet chains.KFC Hot Wings and fries.KFC was founded by Colonel Harland Sanders, an entrepreneur who began selling fried chicken from his roadside restaurant in Corbin, Kentucky, during the Great Depression. Sanders identified the potential of the restaurant franchising concept, and the first 'Kentucky Fried Chicken' franchise opened in Utah in 1952. KFC popularized chicken in the fast food industry, diversifying the market by challenging the established dominance of the hamburger. By branding himself as 'Colonel Sanders', Harland became a prominent figure of American cultural history, and his image remains widely used in KFC advertising to this day. However, the company's rapid expansion overwhelmed the aging Sanders, and he sold it to a group of investors led by John Y. Brown Jr. and Jack C. Massey in 1964.

giftCards.name: Dark Forest Tour In Munnar
giftCards.desc: - Munnar is a land of beauty combined with some of the most inexplicable examples of mystery. On the list of these adventures is this trekking trail of the dark forest. - The place is named so because the canopy of trees is so thick that even in broad daylight, it remains pitch dark inside. This adds to the thrill of walking in the hills as you make your way through the forests. - Venturing onto some of the trickiest trekking routes of Munnar, and towards the end of the tour, the guide will also take you on tea plantation tour, adding an aromatic touch to the tour.

giftCards.name: Tree House Stay At Seven Springs Plantation Resort, Munnar
giftCards.desc: Just 15 minutes’ drive away from Munnar bus station, the Seven Springs Plantation Resort is a place surrounded cardamom plantation and forests on all sides. The resort is the perfect base camp for trekkers and peace seekers. Located atop a hill, the resort has a perfect view of Idukki Arch Dam (Asia’s biggest arch dam). Made of all wooden materials, the tree house of the resort is located 30 feet above ground, and comes decked with LED TV, Mini fridge, Coffee/tea maker, luxury mattresses, Intercom & attached luxury toilets. Covered with ethnic furnishings, the tree house also has wooden staircases, secured and checked for the safety of elderly and children.

giftCards.name: Overnight Stay At K Gudi Wilderness Camp Near Mysore
giftCards.desc: Visit this beautiful wilderness camps of Kyathadevara Gudi, located amidst the mesmerising scenery, away from the hustle and bustle of city life. Reach the resort and check in at around 12:30 PM and start your day of relaxation. In the afternoon at around 01:30 PM have a sumptuous lunch. At around 03:30, sip a cup of tea or coffee and get ready for a jungle adventure in a jeep as you encounter gaur families, herds of elephants, bears, or a leopard perched on a tree. Witness the amazing wildlife show and learn about the laws of the jungle through others’ experiences at around 06:45 PM. In the evening at around 08:30 PM sit comfortably around the campfire and enjoy a delicious dinner. Next day, wake up early morning at around 06:00 AM and enjoy a cup of hot coffee. Again embark on the jungle safari at around 06:15 till 08:30 AM. Enjoy a sumptuous breakfast after your jeep safari and conclude your unforgettable trip to the nature camp at around 11:00 AM. The camp can accommodate thirty to forty guests at a time and it comprises 8 tented cottages, 3 log huts and 2 well-furnished family rooms at the Maharaja’s Hunting Lodge.

giftCards.name: Trekking In Kudremukh In Karnataka
giftCards.desc: Jeeps tread through the craggy terrains to reach the base camp, with the thrilling ride going through coffee estates and scenic waterfalls. Trekking 11 kilometers through the rainforests unravels nature's splendour, as multiple streams, views of towering peaks, and a 30-foot waterfall astound you before the Kudremukh peak is reached. More rugged Jeep rides are in store, with a walk till the Somavati stream leading to the serene confluence point of the Bhadra and Tungabhadra rivers. A visit to the coffee farms is another way to experience the transcendental beauty of the vicinity. And if luck is on your side, you might even be able to spot some of the wildlife species!

giftCards.name: Sakleshpur 2 Day Adventure
giftCards.desc: Sakleshpur is a hill station town and headquarters of Sakleshpur Taluk in Hassan district in the South Indian state of Karnataka. The town lies in the Malnad region on the magnificent hills of the biodiversity hotspot, the Western Ghats. It has an average elevation of 949 metres (3113 feet). Hemavathi river flows in Sakleshpur town. The southern range, which includes Bisle reserve forest and the region around Sakleshpur is listed as one of the 18 most diverse spots in the world in terms of flora and fauna.

giftCards.name: Paragliding In Kullu Manali
giftCards.desc: Experience an amazing paragliding ride in the skies of Manali and Kullu Valley on your next holiday with your family and friends. Experienced pilots will offer you both single and tandem rides for this experience and will take you on both short and long flights across the Kulu Valley. The short fly will be for 15 minutes and you will get to enjoy a birds-eye view of the beautiful hills and valleys of Kulu and Manali. The take-off site is at Dhobi, which is a new age, offbeat paragliding site and is now gaining popularity. It is located at about 20 kms from Kullu and you can reach here by either taking a public transport or by hiring a private cab The equipment you will need is imported from France and are tested for safety.

giftCards.name: Camp Riverwild In Jim Corbett
giftCards.desc: Camping in the wild boasts all the features of an exceptional jungle Retreat such as beautiful setting, excellent cuisine and abundant wildlife. It is located on the fringes of the Corbett Park and on the banks of the river Kosi- providing an exotic scenic view. Thatched roofs, wooden and stone finishes complete the picture of this getaway. Relax, read and soak in the warmth and vibrancy of camp is an ideal Jungle retreat for friends, families or small groups. Get your meals served on fine Indian pottery and you can make your own menu with the Executive Chef here. Adventurous wildlife safaris along with a guide make this place a truly memorable experience and highlight of your holiday.

giftCards.name: Boutique Resort Stay In Nainital
giftCards.desc: An impeccable union of the bygone era and contemporary style, the Resort near Nainital, is just the place to stay, celebrate and interact with your loved ones in nature's heart. This unique boutique resort is a mesmerizing destination boasting a plethora of inspiring spaces along with nature's opulence. Live the golden period while you experience bliss in the lush landscape of Uttarakhand.  It is gifted with numerous calm sit-outs where guests can spend amazing time with their dear ones.

giftCards.name: Get 50% Off on KFC
giftCards.desc: Get 50% off at any KFC store on shop for 999 and above.KFC, also known as Kentucky Fried Chicken, is an American fast food restaurant chain headquartered in Louisville, Kentucky that specializes in fried chicken. It is the world's second-largest restaurant chain (as measured by sales) after McDonald's, with 22,621 locations globally in 136 countries as of December 2018. The chain is a subsidiary of Yum! Brands, a restaurant company that also owns the Pizza Hut, Taco Bell, and WingStreet chains.KFC Hot Wings and fries.KFC was founded by Colonel Harland Sanders, an entrepreneur who began selling fried chicken from his roadside restaurant in Corbin, Kentucky, during the Great Depression. Sanders identified the potential of the restaurant franchising concept, and the first 'Kentucky Fried Chicken' franchise opened in Utah in 1952. KFC popularized chicken in the fast food industry, diversifying the market by challenging the established dominance of the hamburger. By branding himself as 'Colonel Sanders', Harland became a prominent figure of American cultural history, and his image remains widely used in KFC advertising to this day. However, the company's rapid expansion overwhelmed the aging Sanders, and he sold it to a group of investors led by John Y. Brown Jr. and Jack C. Massey in 1964.

giftCards.name: Flat 40% Off on Zomato orders
giftCards.desc: Flat 40% OFF on online transaction from select restaurants.Minimum order value of Rs 99 is required.Maximum savings of Rs 100.Zomato is an restaurant search and discovery service founded in 2008 by Deepinder Goyal and Pankaj Chaddah. It currently operates in 24 countries. It provides information and reviews of restaurants, including images of menus where the restaurant does not have its own website and also online delivery.The restaurant search and discovery platform began its operations under the name, Foodiebay. In November 2010, the brand was renamed as Zomato.By 2011, Zomato launched in Bengaluru, Pune, Chennai, Hyderabad, [[Ahmedabad] [Gandhidham]]. With the introduction of .xxx domains in 2011, Zomato also launched zomato.xxx, a site dedicated to food porn. The company launched a print version of the website content named, 'Citibank Zomato Restaurant Guide', in collaboration with Citibank in May 2012, but it has since been discontinued.
